PN,37601
SC,0001
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F376A1780693876
OL,3,CPartner of Valdo Calocane stab victim
OL,4,C'lost all trust in NHS and police'
OL,6,FThe partner of a school caretaker who
OL,7,Fwas stabbed to death by paranoid
OL,8,Fschizophrenic Valdo Calocane said she
OL,9,Fhas lost all trust in the NHS and
OL,10,Fpolice.
OL,12,FElaine Newton, whose long-term partner
OL,13,FIan Coates was killed on his way to
OL,14,Fwork in Nottingham, said that hearing
OL,15,Fthe extent of systemic failings during
OL,16,Fthe inquiry into Calocane's attacks
OL,17,Fhas been "horrifying".
OL,26,@yD@JOUyD@UO]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G1/9
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,377,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37602
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F376A1780693876
OL,3,CPartner of Valdo Calocane stab victim
OL,4,C'lost all trust in NHS and police'
OL,6,FMr Coates, 65, was fatally stabbed
OL,7,Fjust over an hour after 19-year-old
OL,8,Fundergraduates Barnaby Webber and
OL,9,FGrace O'Malley-Kumar were killed by
OL,10,FCalocane in the early hours of June 13
OL,11,F2023.
OL,13,FThe inquiry heard it took 91 minutes
OL,14,Ffrom when the first call was made to
OL,15,FNottinghamshire Police about the
OL,16,Fattack on the students at about 4am
OL,17,Funtil Calocane was found and arrested,
OL,18,Fby which time he had killed Mr Coates.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G2/9
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,377,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37603
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F376A1780693876
OL,3,CPartner of Valdo Calocane stab victim
OL,4,C'lost all trust in NHS and police'
OL,6,FThe force's then assistant chief
OL,7,Fconstable Rob Griffin told the inquiry
OL,8,Fthe co-ordination of the search for
OL,9,FCalocane during the attacks "should
OL,10,Fhave been better".
OL,12,FMr Coates's body was kept at the crime
OL,13,Fscene for nearly 15 hours while police
OL,14,Fwere investigating, the inquiry heard,
OL,15,Fand he was covered in blankets for two
OL,16,Fhours until a forensic tent became
OL,17,Favailable.
OL,26,@qD@]OUrD@QO]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G3/9
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,377,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37604
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F376A1780693876
OL,3,CPartner of Valdo Calocane stab victim
OL,4,C'lost all trust in NHS and police'
OL,6,FDuring her evidence to the central
OL,7,FLondon inquiry in March, Ms Newton
OL,8,Fsaid it felt like Mr Coates had been
OL,9,Fkilled twice because she was told he
OL,10,Fhad died in a car crash before being
OL,11,Finformed more than four hours later he
OL,12,Fhad actually been stabbed.
OL,14,FIn a statement on Friday, Ms Newton
OL,15,Fsaid: "After listening to the evidence
OL,16,Fover the last three months, I have
OL,17,Flost all trust in the NHS and the
OL,18,Fpolice."Fundamental issues were
OL,19,Fignored or covered up.
OL,26,@wD@GOUzD@HOU
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G4/9
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,377,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37605
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F376A1780693876
OL,3,CPartner of Valdo Calocane stab victim
OL,4,C'lost all trust in NHS and police'
OL,6,F"Powerful people in positions of trust
OL,7,Fhave lied.
OL,9,F"To hear the full extent of the
OL,10,Fsystemic failings has been horrifying,
OL,11,Fand without the inquiry I don't think
OL,12,Fwe would have ever known just how deep
OL,13,Fthe culture of negligence really is."
OL,15,FMs Newton said it "was not just Valdo
OL,16,FCalocane who killed Ian", adding that
OL,17,Fthe individuals and agencies behind
OL,18,Fthe failings "share that burden of
OL,19,Fresponsibility".
OL,26,@qD@AOUuD@eO]wD@SOUxD@XO]zD@NOU{D@OO]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G5/9
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,377,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37606
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F376A1780693876
OL,3,CPartner of Valdo Calocane stab victim
OL,4,C'lost all trust in NHS and police'
OL,6,F"Three cruel and unnecessary deaths
OL,7,Fare the results of their negligence
OL,8,Fand poor care for the mentally ill,"
OL,9,Fshe added.
OL,11,FCalocane had been sectioned four times
OL,12,Fwhile under the care of
OL,13,FNottinghamshire Healthcare NHS
OL,14,FFoundation Trust (NHFT), before he was
OL,15,Fdischarged to his GP in 2022.
OL,17,FThe inquiry heard he was discharged by
OL,18,Fthe trust's Early Intervention in
OL,19,FPsychosis (EIP) service because he
OL,20,Ffailed to turn up for appointments and
OL,21,Fthe team had "lost" him.
OL,26,@nD@AOUpD@dO]}D@NOU}D@SO]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G6/9
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,377,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37607
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F376A1780693876
OL,3,CPartner of Valdo Calocane stab victim
OL,4,C'lost all trust in NHS and police'
OL,6,FMs Newton continued: "I have lost my
OL,7,Fpartner, my best friend and soulmate.
OL,8,FThe inquiry has shown time and again
OL,9,Fthat it all could have been avoided
OL,10,Fhad the NHS done its duty.
OL,12,F"The system is broken and it can only
OL,13,Fchange if these organisations are
OL,14,Fproperly monitored and truly held to
OL,15,Faccount.
OL,17,F"Those people who concealed the truth
OL,18,Fand or did not fulfil their duty, I
OL,19,Fhope they understand and take
OL,20,Fresponsibility for the irrevocable
OL,21,Fdamage they have caused so many lives."
OL,26,@nD@VOUtD@AOUyD@AOU}D@gO]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G7/9
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,377,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37608
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F376A1780693876
OL,3,CPartner of Valdo Calocane stab victim
OL,4,C'lost all trust in NHS and police'
OL,6,FNicola Ryan-Donnelly, of Fletchers
OL,7,FSolicitors, which represents Ms
OL,8,FNewton, said: "Elaine has shown
OL,9,Fremarkable strength throughout this
OL,10,Finquiry, in the face of some
OL,11,Funimaginably difficult evidence.
OL,13,F"The catalogue of failings, moral
OL,14,Fshortcomings and deceit have left her
OL,15,Ffeeling deflated and forgotten.
OL,26,@pD@OOUuD@AOU
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G8/9
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,377,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37609
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F376A1780693876
OL,3,CPartner of Valdo Calocane stab victim
OL,4,C'lost all trust in NHS and police'
OL,6,F"We support her calls for those
OL,7,Fresponsible to face full
OL,8,Faccountability and look forward to the
OL,9,Fchair's report. Elaine must now be
OL,10,Fgiven the privacy she needs to
OL,11,Frecover."The inquiry is hearing its
OL,12,Ffinal day of evidence on Friday.
OL,14,FReporting History sees journalists
OL,15,Fjoin News At Ten anchor Tom Bradby to
OL,16,Frevisit their remarkable on-the-day
OL,17,Freports of the defining events of the
OL,18,Fmodern age. Listen to the episodes
OL,19,Fbelow...
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@IO]
